description:
What are the signs that we are living in the end times? One of the signs Jesus warned of is the talk of peace and safety. World leaders are talking of peace and safety as they make plans for a better world and work for religious unity. What was accomplished by the World Alliance for Peace Summit in the push for unity of religions? 

Like a stormy wind rippling the waves, we see the evidence that an enemy is at work and Bible prophecy is being fulfilled. But where is the enemy? Many false flags are being waved to distract us. People are looking everywhere else, but the Bible tells us the enemy is in plain sight. Who are the two key players of Revelation 13 who are acting their parts in these last days? These are the ones to watch if we are to avoid being taken in the snare. 

The final confrontation between Christ and Satan is opening before our eyes. This Gospel ship is heading for Malta and the turbulent waves of persecution, but the ship is under Gods control and none who stay aboard will be lost. 

This introductory lecture sets the stage for an examination of Bible prophecy, history and current world events to show us where we are and where were heading.

Discover more: https://amazingdiscoveries.org
